############################################

### 🔁 RESET DE SENHA

############################################

### 📩 Solicitar reset de senha

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "[joao@gmail.com](mailto:joao@gmail.com)"
}

###

### ❌ Reset com email inexistente (não deve revelar)

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "joao@gmail.com"
}

###

### ⚠️ Cole aqui o token recebido no email/log

@resetToken = 1d66618c-307d-4e82-bb12-df60bebab261

###

### 🔐 Criar nova senha

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/new-password?token={{resetToken}}&newPassword=654321

###

### ❌ Token inválido

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/new-password?token=token_invalido&newPassword=123456

###

### ⏱️ Token expirado (simular alterando no banco)

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/new-password?token={{resetToken}}&newPassword=123456

###

### 🔥 Reutilizar token (deve falhar)

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/new-password?token={{resetToken}}&newPassword=999999

###

############################################

### 🔐 TESTES DE LOGIN APÓS RESET

############################################

### 🔑 Login com nova senha

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "[joao@gmail.com](mailto:joao@gmail.com)",
"password": "654321"
}

###

### ❌ Login com senha antiga (deve falhar)

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "[joao@gmail.com](mailto:joao@gmail.com)",
"password": "123456"
}

###

